org.apache.edgent.streamscope

Class StreamScopeRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.edgent.streamscope.StreamScopeRegistry

  • public class StreamScopeRegistry
extends java.lang.Object
    A registry for Stream "oscilloscope" StreamScope instances.

    The registry contains a collection of StreamScope instances that are registered by one or more names.

    The names are: by a TStream alias or by a stream's (output port's) unique identifier. Static methods are provided for composing these names and extracting the alias/identifier from generated names.

    See Also:
    DevelopmentProvider
